overview.en: BBIN is an effective decentralized block chain underlying basic application platform. Its original intention is to establish a block chain ecosystem. BBIN provides a forward-looking and low-cost industry ecological block chain application solution.
overview.zh: BBIN是一个有效去中心化的区块链底层基础应用平台，其设计初衷是为了建立一个区块链生态系统，BBIN提供一个具有前瞻性的、低成本的行业生态区块链应用解决方案。
